Simple experiments using UDKInstall-2013-07.exe

features:
* 	thirdperson free camera with zoom and shouldercam mode
	(A free third person camera that moves freely from the
	player character and allows the character to face/look
	independent of the camera. Also allows camera to zoom in
	and out and have collision with the environment to prevent
	clipping.)

* 	target lockon system 
	(Button functionality to target lock enemies and make
	player face target. Allows for cycling of targets.)

* 	stamina and stamina recovery system
	(A sprinting system that allows the player to move quicker
	than normal speed and uses stamina to control use of the
	sprinting.)

* 	basic custom AI
	(kismet is not needed, but needs tweaks)

